table.name: EMPLOYEE_WORKBRAIN_USER

checkConstraint.constraint: JOB_RPT_HCTYPE IN ('I','D') OR JOB_RPT_HCTYPE IS NULL

checkConstraint.constraint: (WBG_ID IS NOT NULL AND WBT_ID IS NULL AND CALCGRP_ID IS NULL AND PAYGRP_ID IS NULL ) OR (WBG_ID IS NULL AND WBT_ID IS NOT NULL AND CALCGRP_ID IS NULL AND PAYGRP_ID IS NULL ) OR (WBG_ID IS NULL AND WBT_ID IS NULL AND CALCGRP_ID IS NOT NULL AND PAYGRP_ID IS NULL ) OR (WBG_ID IS NULL AND WBT_ID IS NULL AND CALCGRP_ID IS NULL AND PAYGRP_ID IS NOT NULL )

table.name: SEC_EMPLOYEE
table.viewSql: SELECT EMPLOYEE_TEAM.EMP_ID, WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM.WBU_ID, GREATEST (EMPLOYEE_TEAM.EMPT_START_DATE, WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM.WBUT_START_DATE) START_DATE, LEAST (EMPLOYEE_TEAM.EMPT_END_DATE, WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM.WBUT_END_DATE) END_DATE, EMPLOYEE_TEAM.WBT_ID, EMPLOYEE_TEAM.EMPT_HOME_TEAM, WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM.WBT_ID USER_WBT_ID, WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM.WBROLE_ID, WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM.CLIENT_ID FROM EMPLOYEE_TEAM, WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM, WORKBRAIN_TEAM WORKBRAIN_TEAM_PRN, WORKBRAIN_TEAM WORKBRAIN_TEAM_CHD WHERE EMPLOYEE_TEAM.EMPT_START_DATE <= WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM.WBUT_END_DATE AND WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM.WBUT_START_DATE <= EMPLOYEE_TEAM.EMPT_END_DATE AND WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM.EMP_ID <> EMPLOYEE_TEAM.EMP_ID AND WORKBRAIN_TEAM_PRN.WBT_ID = WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM.WBT_ID AND EMPLOYEE_TEAM.WBT_ID = WORKBRAIN_TEAM_CHD.WBT_ID AND WORKBRAIN_TEAM_CHD.WBT_LFT BETWEEN WORKBRAIN_TEAM_PRN.WBT_LFT AND WORKBRAIN_TEAM_PRN.WBT_RGT AND WORKBRAIN_TEAM_CHD.WBT_RGT BETWEEN WORKBRAIN_TEAM_PRN.WBT_LFT AND WORKBRAIN_TEAM_PRN.WBT_RGT UNION ALL SELECT EMPLOYEE_TEAM.EMP_ID, WBU_ID, EMPT_START_DATE, EMPT_END_DATE, WBT_ID, EMPT_HOME_TEAM, WBT_ID, 0, EMPLOYEE_TEAM.CLIENT_ID FROM EMPLOYEE_TEAM, WORKBRAIN_USER WHERE EMPLOYEE_TEAM.EMP_ID = WORKBRAIN_USER.EMP_ID AND WORKBRAIN_USER.WBU_CANSEE_SELF = 'Y'

table.name: SEC_EMPLOYEE_BASE
table.viewSql: SELECT EMPLOYEE_TEAM.EMP_ID, WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM.WBU_ID, GREATEST (EMPLOYEE_TEAM.EMPT_START_DATE, WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM.WBUT_START_DATE) START_DATE, LEAST (EMPLOYEE_TEAM.EMPT_END_DATE, WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM.WBUT_END_DATE) END_DATE, EMPLOYEE_TEAM.WBT_ID, EMPLOYEE_TEAM.EMPT_HOME_TEAM, WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM.WBT_ID USER_WBT_ID, WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM.WBROLE_ID, WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM.CLIENT_ID FROM EMPLOYEE_TEAM, WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM WHERE EMPLOYEE_TEAM.EMPT_START_DATE <= WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM.WBUT_END_DATE AND WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM.WBUT_START_DATE <= EMPLOYEE_TEAM.EMPT_END_DATE AND WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM.EMP_ID <> EMPLOYEE_TEAM.EMP_ID AND EMPLOYEE_TEAM.WBT_ID IN (SELECT T2.WBT_ID FROM WORKBRAIN_TEAM T1, WORKBRAIN_TEAM T2 WHERE T2.WBT_LFT >= T1.WBT_LFT AND T2.WBT_LFT <= T1.WBT_RGT AND T1.WBT_ID=WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM.WBT_ID ) UNION ALL SELECT EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID, WBU_ID, EMPT_START_DATE, EMPT_END_DATE, WBT_ID, EMPT_HOME_TEAM, WBT_ID, 0, EMPLOYEE.CLIENT_ID FROM EMPLOYEE, EMPLOYEE_TEAM, WORKBRAIN_USER WHERE EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID = EMPLOYEE_TEAM.EMP_ID AND EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID = WORKBRAIN_USER.EMP_ID AND WORKBRAIN_USER.WBU_CANSEE_SELF = 'Y' AND EMPT_HOME_TEAM = 'Y'

table.name: SEC_EMPLOYEE_DATE
table.viewSql: SELECT EMPLOYEE_TEAM.EMP_ID, WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM.WBU_ID, EMPLOYEE_TEAM.WBT_ID, EMPLOYEE_TEAM.EMPT_HOME_TEAM, WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM.WBT_ID USER_WBT_ID, WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM.WBROLE_ID, WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM.CLIENT_ID, EMPLOYEE_TEAM.EMPT_START_DATE, WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM.WBUT_START_DATE, EMPLOYEE_TEAM.EMPT_END_DATE, WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM.WBUT_END_DATE FROM EMPLOYEE_TEAM, WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM, WORKBRAIN_TEAM WORKBRAIN_TEAM_PRN, WORKBRAIN_TEAM WORKBRAIN_TEAM_CHD WHERE EMPLOYEE_TEAM.EMPT_START_DATE <= WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM.WBUT_END_DATE AND WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM.WBUT_START_DATE <= EMPLOYEE_TEAM.EMPT_END_DATE AND WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM.EMP_ID <> EMPLOYEE_TEAM.EMP_ID AND WORKBRAIN_TEAM_PRN.WBT_ID = WORKBRAIN_USER_TEAM.WBT_ID AND EMPLOYEE_TEAM.WBT_ID = WORKBRAIN_TEAM_CHD.WBT_ID AND WORKBRAIN_TEAM_CHD.WBT_LFT BETWEEN WORKBRAIN_TEAM_PRN.WBT_LFT AND WORKBRAIN_TEAM_PRN.WBT_RGT AND WORKBRAIN_TEAM_CHD.WBT_RGT BETWEEN WORKBRAIN_TEAM_PRN.WBT_LFT AND WORKBRAIN_TEAM_PRN.WBT_RGT UNION ALL SELECT EMPLOYEE_TEAM.EMP_ID, WBU_ID, WBT_ID, EMPT_HOME_TEAM, WBT_ID, 0, EMPLOYEE_TEAM.CLIENT_ID, EMPT_START_DATE, EMPT_START_DATE, EMPT_END_DATE, EMPT_END_DATE FROM EMPLOYEE_TEAM, WORKBRAIN_USER WHERE EMPLOYEE_TEAM.EMP_ID = WORKBRAIN_USER.EMP_ID AND WORKBRAIN_USER.WBU_CANSEE_SELF = 'Y'

table.name: SEC_EMPLOYEE_NR
table.viewSql: SELECT EMP_ID, WBU_ID, MIN( START_DATE ) START_DATE, MAX( END_DATE ) END_DATE, WBT_ID, EMPT_HOME_TEAM, USER_WBT_ID, CLIENT_ID FROM SEC_EMPLOYEE GROUP BY EMP_ID, WBU_ID, WBT_ID, EMPT_HOME_TEAM, USER_WBT_ID, CLIENT_ID

table.name: VIEW_DAY_PART_BY_TEAM
table.viewSql: WITH TEAM_DP_SET (WBT_ID, WBT_PARENT_ID, DPSET_ID, INHERIT, TIER) AS ( SELECT WBT.WBT_ID, WBT.WBT_PARENT_ID, TDPS.DPSET_ID, NVL(TDPS.TMDP_APL_SUBTM, 'N') APPLY_SUBTEAMS, 0 TIER FROM WORKBRAIN_TEAM WBT, TEAM_DAY_PART_SET TDPS WHERE WBT.WBT_ID = TDPS.WBT_ID UNION ALL SELECT WBT.WBT_ID, WBT.WBT_PARENT_ID, CASE WHEN TS.INHERIT = 'Y' THEN TS.DPSET_ID ELSE (SELECT DPSET_ID FROM TEAM_DAY_PART_SET WHERE WBT_ID = -1) END, TS.INHERIT, TS.TIER + 1 FROM WORKBRAIN_TEAM WBT, TEAM_DP_SET TS WHERE WBT.WBT_PARENT_ID = TS.WBT_ID AND NOT WBT.WBT_ID IN (SELECT WBT_ID FROM TEAM_DAY_PART_SET) AND WBT.WBT_ID <> WBT.WBT_PARENT_ID ) SELECT DP.DP_ID, DP.DP_NAME, DP.DP_DESC, DP.DP_START_TIME, DP.DP_END_TIME, DP.DP_FLAG1, DP.DP_FLAG2, DP.DP_FLAG3, DP.DP_FLAG4, DP.DP_FLAG5, DP.DP_UDF1, DP.DP_UDF2, DP.DP_UDF3, DP.DP_UDF4, DP.DP_UDF5, DP.DPSET_ID, DP.DP_HIDE, DP.DP_SHORT_CODE, DP.IS_FIRST_DP, DP.DP_SORT_ORDER, TDPS.WBT_ID FROM TEAM_DP_SET TDPS, DAY_PART DP WHERE DP.DPSET_ID = TDPS.DPSET_ID

table.name: VIEW_ES_ROTATION_DAYPART
table.viewSql: ( SELECT ES_ROTATION_VERSION.rotvr_id, DAY_PART.DP_ID, 1 FROM ES_ROTATION_VERSION , ES_ROTATION , DAY_PART , ( -- GET DAY PART SET FROM SETUP SELECT TEAM_DAY_PART_SET.WBT_ID,DPSET_ID DPSET_ID FROM TEAM_DAY_PART_SET UNION -- GET DAY PART SET FROM PARENT SELECT ES_ROTATION.WBT_ID ,DPSET_ID FROM TEAM_DAY_PART_SET , SEC_WB_TEAM_CHILD_PARENT , ES_ROTATION WHERE SEC_WB_TEAM_CHILD_PARENT.PARENT_WBT_ID = TEAM_DAY_PART_SET.WBT_ID AND ES_ROTATION.WBT_ID = SEC_WB_TEAM_CHILD_PARENT.CHILD_WBT_ID AND TEAM_DAY_PART_SET.TMDP_APL_SUBTM = 'Y' AND SEC_WB_TEAM_CHILD_PARENT.CHILD_WBT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT WBT_ID FROM TEAM_DAY_PART_SET ) UNION -- GET DAYPART FROM DEFAULT SELECT ES_ROTATION.WBT_ID ,DPSET_ID FROM TEAM_DAY_PART_SET , SEC_WB_TEAM_CHILD_PARENT , ES_ROTATION WHERE SEC_WB_TEAM_CHILD_PARENT.PARENT_WBT_ID = TEAM_DAY_PART_SET.WBT_ID AND ES_ROTATION.WBT_ID = SEC_WB_TEAM_CHILD_PARENT.CHILD_WBT_ID AND TEAM_DAY_PART_SET.DPSET_ID = 1 -- DEFAULT AND SEC_WB_TEAM_CHILD_PARENT.CHILD_WBT_ID NOT IN (SELECT WBT_ID FROM TEAM_DAY_PART_SET UNION SELECT ES_ROTATION.WBT_ID FROM TEAM_DAY_PART_SET , SEC_WB_TEAM_CHILD_PARENT , ES_ROTATION WHERE SEC_WB_TEAM_CHILD_PARENT.PARENT_WBT_ID = TEAM_DAY_PART_SET.WBT_ID AND ES_ROTATION.WBT_ID = SEC_WB_TEAM_CHILD_PARENT.CHILD_WBT_ID AND TEAM_DAY_PART_SET.TMDP_APL_SUBTM = 'Y' ) ) TEAM_DP_SET WHERE ES_ROTATION_VERSION.ROT_ID = ES_ROTATION.ROT_ID AND ES_ROTATION.WBT_ID = TEAM_DP_SET.WBT_ID AND DAY_PART.DPSET_ID = TEAM_DP_SET.DPSET_ID )

table.name: VIEW_MOD_DAILY_SUMMARY
table.viewSql: select emp_lastname || ',' || emp_firstname || ' (' || emp_name || ')' emp_info, employee.emp_id, wrks_work_date, decode(to_char(wrks_start_time, 'hh24:mi'),'00:00','-', to_char(wrks_start_time, 'hh24:mi')) "START", decode(to_char(wrks_end_time, 'hh24:mi'),'00:00','-', to_char(wrks_end_time, 'hh24:mi')) "END", wrks_authorized auth, Reg, OT, DT, Reg + OT + DT total, EMPLOYEE.CLIENT_ID from employee, view_mod_daily_summary_base2 where employee.emp_id = view_mod_daily_summary_base2.emp_id

table.name: VIEW_MOD_DAILY_SUMMARY_BASE
table.viewSql: select sum(wrkd_minutes) wrkd_minutes, emp_id, wrks_work_date, wrks_start_time, wrks_end_time, htype_name, tcode_name, wrkd_type, decode(wrks_authorized,'Y','*',null) wrks_authorized, 1 from work_summary, work_detail, hour_type, time_code where work_summary.wrks_id = work_detail.wrks_id(+) and work_detail.htype_id = hour_type.htype_id (+) and work_detail.tcode_id = time_code.tcode_id (+) group by emp_id, wrks_work_date, wrks_start_time, wrks_end_time, htype_name, wrkd_type, tcode_name, wrks_authorized

table.name: VIEW_MOD_DAILY_SUMMARY_BASE2
table.viewSql: select emp_id, wrks_work_date, wrks_start_time, wrks_end_time, sum(decode(htype_name,'REG', wrkd_minutes, 0)) Reg, sum(decode(htype_name,'OT1.5', wrkd_minutes,'OT1', wrkd_minutes, 0)) OT, sum(decode(htype_name,'OT2', wrkd_minutes, 0)) DT, wrks_authorized, 1 from view_mod_daily_summary_base,time_code where view_mod_daily_summary_base.tcode_name = time_code.tcode_name group by emp_id, wrks_work_date, wrks_start_time, wrks_end_time, wrks_authorized

table.name: VIEW_MOD_DISTLIST_MEMBERS

table.viewSql: SELECT EMPLOYEE_OVERTIME.EMPOT_ID, EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID, SUM(NVL(EMPLOYEE_OVERTIME.EMPOT_OFFERED, 0)) EMPOT_OFFERED, SUM(NVL(EMPLOYEE_OVERTIME.EMPOT_REFUSED, 0)) EMPOT_REFUSED, SUM(NVL(EMPLOYEE_OVERTIME.EMPOT_WORKED, 0)) EMPOT_WORKED, NVL(EMPLOYEE_OVERTIME.EMPOT_WORK_DATE, TRUNC(SYSDATE)) EMPOT_WORK_DATE, EMPLOYEE.EMP_NAME, EMPLOYEE.EMP_SENIORITY_DATE, EMPLOYEE.EMP_LASTNAME, EMPLOYEE.EMP_FIRSTNAME, 1 FROM EMPLOYEE_OVERTIME, EMPLOYEE WHERE EMPLOYEE_OVERTIME.EMP_ID (+)=EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID AND EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID > 0 GROUP BY EMPOT_ID, EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID, EMPOT_WORK_DATE, EMP_NAME, EMP_SENIORITY_DATE, EMP_LASTNAME, EMP_FIRSTNAME

TO_DATE (TO_CHAR (MSG_DATE, 'YYYY-MON-DD HH24:MI:SS'), 'YYYY-MON-DD HH24:MI:SS')) - MSGTYP_PERIOD), 1, 0, 1) ALLOW_DEL, MSG.WBU_NAME SND_NAME, -- pkg_msg.msg_url_str function removed for efficency DECODE ( MSG_TYP.MSGTYP_ID, 3, 'messaging/msgDisplay.jsp?' || 'msg_id=' || TO_CHAR (MSG.MSG_ID) || '&' || 'WBU_ID=' || TO_CHAR (USR.WBU_ID) || '&' || 'folder=' || (RCP.MSGFLDR_ID) || '&' || 'fromEmail=true', 6, 'messaging/businessObjectReply.jsp?' || 'MSG_ID=' || TO_CHAR (MSG.MSG_ID) || '&' || 'WBU_ID=' || TO_CHAR (USR.WBU_ID) || '&' || 'folder_id=' || to_char (RCP.MSGFLDR_ID) || '&' || 'newOld=' || RCP.RCPMSG_NEW_OLD || '&' || 'fromEmail=true', 5, 'messaging/businessObject.jsp?' || 'MSG_ID=' || TO_CHAR (MSG.MSG_ID) || '&busObjTyp_id=null&' || 'folder_id=' || to_char (RCP.MSGFLDR_ID) || '&' || 'newOld=' || RCP.RCPMSG_NEW_OLD || '&' || 'fromEmail=true', 8, 'messaging/onlineSurvey.jsp?' || 'MSG_ID=' || TO_CHAR (RCP.MSG_ID) || '&' || 'WBU_ID=' || to_char (USR.WBU_ID ) || '&' || 'fromEmail=true', 9, 'messaging/businessObject.jsp?' || 'MSG_ID=' || TO_CHAR (MSG.MSG_ID) || '&resend=true&' || 'newOld=' || RCP.RCPMSG_NEW_OLD || '&' || 'folder_id=' || to_char (RCP.MSGFLDR_ID) || '&' || 'fromEmail=true', 10,'messaging/onlineTest.jsp?' || 'MSG_ID=' || TO_CHAR (MSG.MSG_ID) || '&' || 'WBU_ID=' || TO_CHAR (USR.WBU_ID) || '&' || 'folder=' || to_char (RCP.MSGFLDR_ID) || '&' || 'fromEmail=true', 7, 'messaging/msgDisplay.jsp?' || 'MSG_ID=' || TO_CHAR (MSG.MSG_ID) || '&' || 'WBU_ID=' || TO_CHAR (USR.WBU_ID) || '&' || 'folder=' || (RCP.MSGFLDR_ID) || '&' || 'fromEmail=true' ) URL_STR, USR.CLIENT_ID FROM RECIPIENT_MESSAGE RCP, MESSAGE MSG, MESSAGE_TYPE MSG_TYP, WORKBRAIN_USER USR WHERE RCP.MSG_ID = MSG.MSG_ID AND MSG.MSGTYP_ID = MSG_TYP.MSGTYP_ID AND USR.WBU_NAME(+) = RCP.WBU_NAME

table.name: VIEW_MOD_TEAM_MEMBERS
table.viewSql: SELECT A.WBT_ID TEAM_ID, WBT.WBT_NAME TEAM_NAME, COUNT(ET1.EMP_ID) MEMBER_NAMES, COUNT(ET1.EMP_ID) MEMBER_IDS, A.WBU_ID MEMBER_ID, 1 FROM ( SELECT ET.WBT_ID, WBU.WBU_ID FROM EMPLOYEE_TEAM ET, WORKBRAIN_USER WBU WHERE ET.EMP_ID = WBU.EMP_ID AND SYSDATE BETWEEN EMPT_START_DATE AND EMPT_END_DATE UNION SELECT SWT.WBT_ID, SWT.WBU_ID FROM SEC_WORKBRAIN_TEAM SWT WHERE SYSDATE BETWEEN WBUT_START_DATE AND WBUT_END_DATE ) A, EMPLOYEE_TEAM ET1, WORKBRAIN_TEAM WBT, WORKBRAIN_USER WBU WHERE A.WBT_ID = ET1.WBT_ID AND A.WBT_ID = WBT.WBT_ID AND ET1.EMP_ID = WBU.EMP_ID AND SYSDATE BETWEEN ET1.EMPT_START_DATE AND ET1.EMPT_END_DATE GROUP BY A.WBT_ID, WBT.WBT_NAME, A.WBU_ID

table.name: VIEW_RETRO_ADJUSTMENTS

table.name: VIEW_SB_SHIFT_PAT

table.name: VIEW_SB_SHIFT_SHFT

table.name: VIEW_SHIFT
table.viewSql: select --auto view created by wbSchemaUpdater SHIFT.SHFT_ID, SHIFT.SHFT_NAME, SHIFT.SHFT_DESC, SHIFT.SHFT_START_TIME, SHIFT.SHFT_END_TIME, SHIFT.SHFTGRP_ID, SHIFT.SHFT_YAG, SHIFT.COLR_ID, SHIFT.SHFT_UDF1, SHIFT.SHFT_UDF2, SHIFT.SHFT_UDF3, SHIFT.SHFT_UDF4, SHIFT.SHFT_UDF5, SHIFT.SHFT_VAL1, SHIFT.SHFT_VAL2, SHIFT.SHFT_VAL3, SHIFT.SHFT_VAL4, SHIFT.SHFT_VAL5, SHIFT.SHFT_FLAG1, SHIFT.SHFT_FLAG2, SHIFT.SHFT_FLAG3, SHIFT.SHFT_FLAG4, SHIFT.SHFT_FLAG5, SHIFT_GROUP.SHFTGRP_NAME, COLOUR.COLR_NAME, SHIFT.CLIENT_ID from SHIFT,SHIFT_GROUP,COLOUR where SHIFT.SHFTGRP_ID = SHIFT_GROUP.SHFTGRP_ID and SHIFT.COLR_ID = COLOUR.COLR_ID

table.name: VIEW_SHIFT_BREAK
table.viewSql: select --auto view created by wbSchemaUpdater SHIFT_BREAK.SHFTBRK_ID, SHIFT_BREAK.SHFTBRK_START_TIME, SHIFT_BREAK.SHFTBRK_END_TIME, SHIFT_BREAK.SHFTBRK_MINUTES, SHIFT_BREAK.SHFT_ID, SHIFT_BREAK.TCODE_ID, SHIFT_BREAK.HTYPE_ID, SHIFT.SHFT_NAME, TIME_CODE.TCODE_NAME, HOUR_TYPE.HTYPE_NAME, SHIFT.CLIENT_ID from SHIFT_BREAK,SHIFT,TIME_CODE,HOUR_TYPE where SHIFT_BREAK.SHFT_ID = SHIFT.SHFT_ID and SHIFT_BREAK.TCODE_ID = TIME_CODE.TCODE_ID and SHIFT_BREAK.HTYPE_ID = HOUR_TYPE.HTYPE_ID

table.name: VIEW_SHIFT_PATTERN
table.viewSql: select --auto view created by wbSchemaUpdater SHIFT_PATTERN.SHFTPAT_ID, SHIFT_PATTERN.SHFTPAT_NAME, SHIFT_PATTERN.SHFTPAT_DESC, SHIFT_PATTERN.SHFTPAT_START_DATE, SHIFT_PATTERN.SHFTPAT_DAY_START_TIME, SHIFT_PATTERN.SHFTGRP_ID, SHIFT_PATTERN.SHFTPAT_UDF1, SHIFT_PATTERN.SHFTPAT_UDF2, SHIFT_PATTERN.SHFTPAT_UDF3, SHIFT_PATTERN.SHFTPAT_UDF4, SHIFT_PATTERN.SHFTPAT_UDF5, SHIFT_PATTERN.SHFTPAT_VAL1, SHIFT_PATTERN.SHFTPAT_VAL2, SHIFT_PATTERN.SHFTPAT_VAL3, SHIFT_PATTERN.SHFTPAT_VAL4, SHIFT_PATTERN.SHFTPAT_VAL5, SHIFT_PATTERN.SHFTPAT_FLAG1, SHIFT_PATTERN.SHFTPAT_FLAG2, SHIFT_PATTERN.SHFTPAT_FLAG3, SHIFT_PATTERN.SHFTPAT_FLAG4, SHIFT_PATTERN.SHFTPAT_FLAG5, SHIFT_GROUP.SHFTGRP_NAME, SHIFT_GROUP.CLIENT_ID from SHIFT_PATTERN,SHIFT_GROUP where SHIFT_PATTERN.SHFTGRP_ID = SHIFT_GROUP.SHFTGRP_ID

table.name: VIEW_SHIFT_PATTERN_SHIFTS

table.name: VIEW_SHIFT_PREMIUM_ZONE
table.viewSql: select --auto view created by wbSchemaUpdater SHIFT_PREMIUM_ZONE.SPZONE_ID, SHIFT_PREMIUM_ZONE.SPZONE_NAME, SHIFT_PREMIUM_ZONE.SPZONE_DESC, SHIFT_PREMIUM_ZONE.SPZONE_START_TIME, SHIFT_PREMIUM_ZONE.SPZONE_END_TIME, SHIFT_PREMIUM_ZONE.TCODE_ID, SHIFT_PREMIUM_ZONE.HTYPE_ID, SHIFT_PREMIUM_ZONE.CALCGRP_NAME, SHIFT_PREMIUM_ZONE.SHFTPAT_NAME, SHIFT_PREMIUM_ZONE.DAYTYP_NAME, SHIFT_PREMIUM_ZONE.SHFT_NAME, SHIFT_PREMIUM_ZONE.SPZONE_RATE, SHIFT_PREMIUM_ZONE.SPZONE_MAX_MINUTES, SHIFT_PREMIUM_ZONE.SPZONE_MAX_DOLLARS, SHIFT_PREMIUM_ZONE.SPZONE_SZS_TIME, SHIFT_PREMIUM_ZONE.SPZONE_SZE_TIME, SHIFT_PREMIUM_ZONE.SPZONE_EZS_TIME, SHIFT_PREMIUM_ZONE.SPZONE_EZE_TIME, TIME_CODE.TCODE_NAME, SHIFT_PREMIUM_ZONE.CLIENT_ID from SHIFT_PREMIUM_ZONE,TIME_CODE where SHIFT_PREMIUM_ZONE.TCODE_ID = TIME_CODE.TCODE_ID

table.name: VIEW_SHIFT_PREMIUM_ZONE_FULL
table.viewSql: SELECT SPZONE_ID, SPZONE_NAME, SPZONE_DESC, SPZONE_START_TIME, SPZONE_END_TIME, TCODE_ID, HTYPE_ID, SPZONE_LBM_PERM, JOB_ID, DEPT_ID, PROJ_ID, DOCK_ID, QUANTITY, SPZONE_POPLT_TIME_FLAG, SPZONE_RATE, SPZONE_PERCENTAGE, SPZONE_RATE_TO_USE, SPZONE_HTYPE_MULTIPLY, SPZONE_OT_MULTIPLY, SPZONE_USE_MINUTES, SPZONE_MAX_MINUTES, SPZONE_MAX_DOLLARS, SPZONE_INCL_TCODE_NAMES, SPZONE_INCL_HTYPE_NAMES, SHFTPAT_NAME, SPZONE_INCL_SHFTPAT_IDS, DAYTYP_NAME, SHFT_NAME, SPZONE_INCL_SHIFT_IDS, SPZONE_INCL_JOB_IDS, SPZONE_INCL_DEPT_IDS, SPZONE_INCL_PROJ_IDS, SPZONE_INCL_DOCK_IDS, SPZONE_MIN_QUANTITY, SPZONE_MAX_QUANTITY, SPZONE_SKD_UNSKD, SPZONE_SHFT_TO_CHK, SPZONE_SZS_TIME, SPZONE_SZE_TIME, SPZONE_EZS_TIME, SPZONE_EZE_TIME, SPZONE_SCH_RNG_STA_TIME, SPZONE_SCH_RNG_END_TIME, SPZONE_MIN_MINUTES, SPZONE_MW_STA_AFT_TIME, SPZONE_MW_BEFORE, SPZONE_MW_AFTER, SPZONE_MW_END_BFR_TIME, SPZONE_MW_MINUTES, SPZONE_MWMIN_START, SPZONE_MWMIN_END, SPZONE_ELIGIBLE_DETAIL_TYPE, CALCGRP_NAME, SPZONE_BEST_OF_GRP, SPZONE_UPDATE_FLDS, SPZONE_APPLY_TYPE, CLIENT_ID FROM SHIFT_PREMIUM_ZONE

table.name: VIEW_SHIFT_TIME
table.viewSql: select es.EmpSkd_Id, to_char(es.work_date, 'mm/dd/yyyy')||' ['|| to_char(es.EmpSkd_Act_Start_Time, 'hh:mi')||'-'|| to_char(es.EmpSkd_Act_end_Time, 'hh:mi') || ']', es.emp_id, es.work_date, ES.CLIENT_ID from employee_schedule es, shift s where es.empskd_act_shift_id = s.shft_id and s.shft_id > 0

table.name: VIEW_SO_ACTSFTHR
table.viewSql: SELECT SO_SHIFT_ACTIVITY.SHFTACT_ID, SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SHFTDET_ID, SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SKD_ID, SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.EMP_ID, SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.JOB_ID, SO_SCHEDULED_SHIFT.SKDSHFT_DATE, CASE WHEN SHFTACT_END_TIME <= SHFTACT_START_TIME AND TO_CHAR(SHFTACT_END_TIME, 'HH24:MI:SS') <> '00:00:00' AND TO_CHAR(SHFTACT_START_TIME, 'HH24:MI:SS') <> '00:00:00' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS MIDNIGHT_ROLLOVER, NVL(JOB.JOB_DESC, JOB.JOB_NAME) AS JOB_DESC, SO_SHIFT_ACTIVITY.SHFTACT_DATE, SO_SHIFT_ACTIVITY.SHFTACT_START_TIME, SO_SHIFT_ACTIVITY.SHFTACT_END_TIME, CASE WHEN SHFTACT_END_TIME - SHFTACT_START_TIME <= 0 THEN TO_NUMBER(TO_CHAR((SHFTACT_END_TIME - SHFTACT_START_TIME + 1) * 24, '99999.99')) ELSE TO_NUMBER(TO_CHAR((SHFTACT_END_TIME - SHFTACT_START_TIME) * 24, '99999.99')) END AS SHFTACT_LEN, SO_SHIFT_ACTIVITY.SKDGRP_ID, SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_NAME, SO_ACTIVITY.ACT_WORKING FROM SO_SHIFT_ACTIVITY, SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP, SO_SHIFT_DETAIL, SO_SCHEDULED_SHIFT, JOB, SO_ACTIVITY WHERE SO_SHIFT_ACTIVITY.SHFTDET_ID=SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SHFTDET_ID AND SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SKDSHFT_ID=SO_SCHEDULED_SHIFT.SKDSHFT_ID AND SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.JOB_ID=JOB.JOB_ID AND SO_SHIFT_ACTIVITY.ACT_ID=SO_ACTIVITY.ACT_ID AND SO_SHIFT_ACTIVITY.SKDGRP_ID = SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_ID (+)

table.name: VIEW_SO_AVAIL_INFO
table.viewSql: SELECT AMXOV_ID, AMX_OVERRIDE.EMP_ID, EMP_LASTNAME, EMP_FIRSTNAME, SO_EMPLOYEE.SEMP_SKDMAX_HRS, EMP_SENIORITY_DATE, EMP_HIRE_DATE, SO_EMPLOYEE.SKDGRP_ID, SO_EMPLOYEE.EMPGRP_ID, SO_EMPLOYEE.SEMP_ONFIXED_SKD, SO_EMPLOYEE.SEMP_IS_SALARY, EMPLOYEE_JOB.JOB_ID, AMX_OVERRIDE.AMXOVC_ID, AMXOVC_DESC, AMXOV_WD_ST, AMXOV_WD_END, AMX_OVERRIDE.AMXOV_MODIFY_DATE, AMX_OVERRIDE.AMXOV_MODIFY_TIME, AMXOV_ST_TIME, AMXOV_END_TIME, AMXOV_COMMENT, AMXOV_APPRV_STATUS, AMX_OVR_CODE.AMXOVC_CNTRBTOCOST, AMX_OVR_CODE.AMXOVC_DAILYCSTHRS, CASE WHEN EMPLOYEE.EMP_BASE_RATE > 0 THEN EMPLOYEE.EMP_BASE_RATE ELSE JOB_TEAM.JOBTEAM_AV_HR_RATE END AS HOURLY_RATE, JOB_TEAM.JOBTEAM_WOT_THRESH FROM AMX_OVERRIDE, AMX_OVR_CODE, EMPLOYEE, SO_EMPLOYEE, EMPLOYEE_JOB, JOB_TEAM WHERE AMX_OVERRIDE.EMP_ID = EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID AND AMX_OVERRIDE.AMXOVC_ID = AMX_OVR_CODE.AMXOVC_ID AND EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID = SO_EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID AND EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID = EMPLOYEE_JOB.EMP_ID AND EMPLOYEE_JOB.JOB_ID = JOB_TEAM.JOB_ID

table.name: VIEW_SO_CL_STFDEF
table.viewSql: SELECT SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_ID, SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_NAME, SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_FCAST_MTD, SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_VOLSUB, SO_VOLUME_TYPE.VOLTYP_DESC, SO_CLIENT_STFDEF.JOB_ID, NVL(JOB.JOB_DESC, JOB.JOB_NAME) AS JOB_DESC, SO_CLIENT_STFDEF.STSKL_ID, NVL(ST_SKILL.STSKL_DESC,ST_SKILL.STSKL_NAME) AS SKL_DESC, SO_CLIENT_STFDEF.SKILL_LEVEL, SO_CLIENT_STFDEF.CSD_MIN_REQ, SO_CLIENT_STFDEF.CSD_MAX_REQ, SO_CLIENT_STFDEF.SHFTSTFREQ_ID, SO_CLIENT_STFDEF.CSD_CONTROL_WRK FROM SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP, SO_VOLUME_TYPE, SO_CLIENT_STFDEF, JOB, ST_SKILL WHERE SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_ID = SO_CLIENT_STFDEF.SKDGRP_ID AND SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.VOLTYP_ID(+) = SO_VOLUME_TYPE.VOLTYP_ID AND SO_CLIENT_STFDEF.JOB_ID = JOB.JOB_ID (+) AND SO_CLIENT_STFDEF.STSKL_ID = ST_SKILL.STSKL_ID (+)

table.name: VIEW_SO_DAILY_SKD
table.viewSql: SELECT SO_SHIFT_ACTIVITY.SHFTACT_ID, SO_SHIFT_ACTIVITY.SHFTACT_DATE, SO_SHIFT_ACTIVITY.SHFTACT_START_TIME, SO_SHIFT_ACTIVITY.SHFTACT_END_TIME, SO_SHIFT_ACTIVITY.ACT_ID, NVL(SO_ACTIVITY.ACT_DESC, SO_ACTIVITY.ACT_NAME) AS ACT_DESC, SO_ACTIVITY.ACT_WORKING, SO_SHIFT_ACTIVITY.SKDGRP_ID, SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_NAME, SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_SORT_ORDER, SO_SHIFT_ACTIVITY.SHFTDET_ID, SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SKD_ID, SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.EMP_ID, EMPLOYEE.EMP_LASTNAME, EMPLOYEE.EMP_FIRSTNAME, SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.JOB_ID, NVL(JOB.JOB_DESC, JOB.JOB_NAME) AS JOB_DESC FROM SO_SHIFT_ACTIVITY, SO_ACTIVITY, SO_SHIFT_DETAIL, EMPLOYEE, JOB, SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP WHERE SO_SHIFT_ACTIVITY.ACT_ID = SO_ACTIVITY.ACT_ID AND SO_SHIFT_ACTIVITY.SKDGRP_ID = SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_ID (+) AND SO_SHIFT_ACTIVITY.SHFTDET_ID = SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SHFTDET_ID AND SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.EMP_ID = EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID AND SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.JOB_ID = JOB.JOB_ID

table.name: VIEW_SO_DAY_RES
table.viewSql: SELECT SKDGRP_ID, RESDET_DATE, SUM(RESDET_VOLUME) AS DAILY_VOLUME, 1 AS INVTYP_ID FROM SO_RESULTS_DETAIL GROUP BY SKDGRP_ID, RESDET_DATE

table.name: VIEW_SO_EMP_CSTDET
table.viewSql: SELECT SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_ID, VIEW_SO_EMPPAYROLL.EMP_ID, VIEW_SO_EMPPAYROLL.WRKS_WORK_DATE, NVL(VIEW_SO_EMPPAYROLL.REG_HOURS,0) AS REG_HOURS, NVL(VIEW_SO_EMPPAYROLL.OT_HOURS,0) AS OT_HOURS, VIEW_SO_EMP_POS.JOB_ID, NVL(VIEW_SO_EMP_POS.HOURLY_RATE,0) AS HOURLY_RATE, NVL(VIEW_SO_EMP_POS.JOBTEAM_OT_MULT,0) AS JOBTEAM_OT_MULT, NVL(VIEW_SO_EMP_POS.JOBTEAM_OT_INC,0) AS JOBTEAM_OT_INC, (NVL(VIEW_SO_EMP_POS.HOURLY_RATE,0) * NVL(REG_HOURS,0)) + (NVL(VIEW_SO_EMP_POS.HOURLY_RATE,0) * NVL(OT_HOURS,0) * (NVL(VIEW_SO_EMP_POS.JOBTEAM_OT_MULT,0) / 100) ) + (NVL(OT_HOURS, 0) * NVL(VIEW_SO_EMP_POS.JOBTEAM_OT_INC,0)) AS EMPLOYEE_PAY FROM SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP, SO_EMPLOYEE, VIEW_SO_EMPPAYROLL, VIEW_SO_EMP_POS WHERE SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_ID = SO_EMPLOYEE.SKDGRP_ID AND SO_EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID = VIEW_SO_EMPPAYROLL.EMP_ID AND SO_EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID = VIEW_SO_EMP_POS.EMP_ID

table.name: VIEW_SO_EMP_POS
table.viewSql: SELECT EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID, EMPLOYEE.EMP_LASTNAME, EMPLOYEE.EMP_FIRSTNAME, EMPLOYEE.EMP_SENIORITY_DATE, SO_EMPLOYEE.SEMP_IS_SALARY, SO_EMPLOYEE.SEMP_ONFIXED_SKD, SO_EMPLOYEE.SKDGRP_ID, SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_NAME, SO_EMPLOYEE.EMPGRP_ID, SO_EMPLOYEE.SEMP_SKDMAX_HRS, NVL(SO_EMPLOYEE_GROUP.EMPGRP_DESC,SO_EMPLOYEE_GROUP.EMPGRP_NAME) AS EMPGRP_DESC, JOB.JOB_ID, NVL(JOB.JOB_DESC,JOB.JOB_NAME) AS JOB_DESC, EMPLOYEE_JOB.EMPJOB_START_DATE, EMPLOYEE_JOB.EMPJOB_END_DATE, CASE WHEN EMPLOYEE.EMP_BASE_RATE > 0 THEN EMP_BASE_RATE ELSE JOB_TEAM.JOBTEAM_AV_HR_RATE END AS HOURLY_RATE, CASE WHEN SO_EMPLOYEE.SEMP_ONFIXED_SKD = 1 AND SO_EMPLOYEE.SEMP_IS_SALARY = 1 THEN 24 ELSE JOBTEAM_DOT_THRESH END AS JOBTEAM_DOT_THRESH, JOBTEAM_WOT_THRESH, JOBTEAM_OT_INC, JOBTEAM_OT_MULT, EMP_STATUS FROM EMPLOYEE, EMPLOYEE_JOB, JOB, SO_EMPLOYEE, SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP, SO_EMPLOYEE_GROUP, JOB_TEAM WHERE EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID = EMPLOYEE_JOB.EMP_ID AND EMPLOYEE_JOB.JOB_ID = JOB.JOB_ID AND EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID = SO_EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID AND SO_EMPLOYEE.SKDGRP_ID = SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_ID AND SO_EMPLOYEE.EMPGRP_ID = SO_EMPLOYEE_GROUP.EMPGRP_ID AND JOB.JOB_ID = JOB_TEAM.JOB_ID AND EMPLOYEE_JOB.EMPJOB_PREFERRED='Y'

table.name: VIEW_SO_EMP_WORK
table.viewSql: SELECT WORKED.EMP_ID, WORKED.JOB_ID, SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_ID, SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SHFTDET_WRK_LOC, WORKED.WRKS_WORK_DATE, NVL(WORKED.REG_HOURS,0) AS REG_HOURS, NVL(WORKED.REG_RATE,0) AS REG_RATE, NVL(WORKED.OT_HOURS,0) AS OT_HOURS, NVL(WORKED.OT_RATE,0) AS OT_RATE, (NVL(WORKED.REG_RATE,0) * NVL(WORKED.REG_HOURS,0)) + (NVL(WORKED.OT_RATE,0) * NVL(WORKED.OT_HOURS,0) ) AS EMPLOYEE_PAY, SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SKD_ID FROM SO_SCHEDULED_SHIFT, SO_SHIFT_DETAIL, SO_EMPLOYEE, SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP, ( SELECT WS.EMP_ID, WD.JOB_ID, WD.WRKD_ID, WS.WRKS_WORK_DATE, DECODE(HT.HTYPE_MULTIPLE, 0, WD.WRKD_RATE, 1, WD.WRKD_RATE, 0) AS REG_RATE, DECODE(HT.HTYPE_MULTIPLE, 0, WD.WRKD_MINUTES/60, 1, WD.WRKD_MINUTES/60, 0) AS REG_HOURS, DECODE(HT.HTYPE_MULTIPLE, 1, 0, 0, 0, WD.WRKD_RATE) AS OT_RATE, DECODE(HT.HTYPE_MULTIPLE, 1, 0, 0, 0, WD.WRKD_MINUTES/60) AS OT_HOURS FROM WORK_SUMMARY WS, WORK_DETAIL WD, HOUR_TYPE HT WHERE WS.WRKS_ID = WD.WRKS_ID AND HT.HTYPE_ID = WD.HTYPE_ID ) WORKED WHERE SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SKDSHFT_ID = SO_SCHEDULED_SHIFT.SKDSHFT_ID AND SO_SCHEDULED_SHIFT.SKDSHFT_DATE = WORKED.WRKS_WORK_DATE AND SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.EMP_ID = WORKED.EMP_ID AND SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.JOB_ID = WORKED.JOB_ID AND SO_EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID = WORKED.EMP_ID AND SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_ID = SO_EMPLOYEE.SKDGRP_ID

table.name: VIEW_SO_EMP_WSUPP
table.viewSql: SELECT SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_ID AS SKDGRP_ID, SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_NAME AS SKDGRP_NAME, EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID FROM SO_EMPLOYEE, EMPLOYEE, SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP WHERE SO_EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID = EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID AND SO_EMPLOYEE.SKDGRP_ID = SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_ID

table.name: VIEW_SO_EMPPAYROLL
table.viewSql: SELECT REG.EMP_ID, REG.WRKS_WORK_DATE, REG.HOURS AS REG_HOURS, OT.HOURS AS OT_HOURS FROM ( SELECT WS.EMP_ID, WS.WRKS_WORK_DATE, SUM(WD.WRKD_MINUTES)/60 AS HOURS FROM WORK_SUMMARY WS, WORK_DETAIL WD, HOUR_TYPE HT WHERE WS.WRKS_ID = WD.WRKS_ID AND HT.HTYPE_ID = WD.HTYPE_ID AND HT.HTYPE_MULTIPLE <= 1 GROUP BY WS.EMP_ID, WS.WRKS_WORK_DATE) REG, ( SELECT WS.EMP_ID, WS.WRKS_WORK_DATE, SUM(WD.WRKD_MINUTES)/60 AS HOURS FROM WORK_SUMMARY WS, WORK_DETAIL WD, HOUR_TYPE HT WHERE WS.WRKS_ID = WD.WRKS_ID AND HT.HTYPE_ID = WD.HTYPE_ID AND HT.HTYPE_MULTIPLE > 1 GROUP BY WS.EMP_ID, WS.WRKS_WORK_DATE) OT WHERE REG.EMP_ID = OT.EMP_ID (+) AND REG.WRKS_WORK_DATE = OT.WRKS_WORK_DATE (+)

table.name: VIEW_SO_EMPPOS_SKL
table.viewSql: SELECT EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID, SO_EMPLOYEE.EMPGRP_ID, EMPLOYEE.EMP_FIRSTNAME, EMPLOYEE.EMP_LASTNAME, SO_EMPLOYEE_GROUP.SKDGRP_ID, NVL(SO_EMPLOYEE_GROUP.EMPGRP_DESC,SO_EMPLOYEE_GROUP.EMPGRP_NAME) AS EMPGRP_DESC, EMPLOYEE_JOB.JOB_ID, ST_EMP_SKILL.STSKL_ID, SO_EMPLOYEE.SEMP_ONFIXED_SKD, EMPLOYEE.EMP_SENIORITY_DATE, EMPLOYEE.EMP_HIRE_DATE, NVL(JOB.JOB_DESC, JOB.JOB_NAME) AS JOB_DESC, NVL(STSKL_DESC, STSKL_NAME) AS SKL_DESC, STEMPSKL_WEIGHT AS SKILL_LEVEL, EMP_FULLTIME, SO_EMPLOYEE.SEMP_SKDMAX_HRS, SO_EMPLOYEE.SEMP_SKDMIN_HRS, SO_EMPLOYEE.SEMP_DAYMAX_HRS, SO_EMPLOYEE.SEMP_SHFTMIN_HRS, EMPLOYEE.EMP_STATUS FROM EMPLOYEE, ST_EMP_SKILL, ST_SKILL, EMPLOYEE_JOB, SO_EMPLOYEE, SO_EMPLOYEE_GROUP, JOB WHERE EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID = EMPLOYEE_JOB.EMP_ID AND EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID = SO_EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID AND SO_EMPLOYEE.EMPGRP_ID = SO_EMPLOYEE_GROUP.EMPGRP_ID AND EMPLOYEE_JOB.JOB_ID = JOB.JOB_ID AND ST_EMP_SKILL.STSKL_ID = ST_SKILL.STSKL_ID AND EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID = ST_EMP_SKILL.EMP_ID

table.name: VIEW_SO_FCAST_DET
table.viewSql: SELECT SO_FCAST.FCAST_ID, SO_FCAST.SKDGRP_ID, SO_FCAST.FCAST_ORIG_ADJPCT, SO_FCAST.FCAST_BUDG_TYP, SO_FCAST.FCAST_BUDG_VAL, SO_FCAST.INVTYP_ID, SO_FCAST_DETAIL.FCASTDET_ID, SO_FCAST_DETAIL.DIST_ID, SO_FCAST_DETAIL.FCAST_ADJVAL, SO_FCAST_DETAIL.FCAST_ADJTYP, SO_FCAST_DETAIL.FCAST_CALLS, SO_FCAST_DETAIL.FCAST_DATE FROM SO_FCAST, SO_FCAST_DETAIL WHERE SO_FCAST.FCAST_ID = SO_FCAST_DETAIL.FCAST_ID

table.name: VIEW_SO_INT_REQ
table.viewSql: SELECT SO_INTERVAL_REQ.SKDGRP_ID, SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_NAME, SO_INTERVAL_REQ.INTREQ_ID, SO_INTERVAL_REQ.SKD_ID, SO_INTERVAL_REQ.JOB_ID, SO_INTERVAL_REQ.STSKL_ID, SO_INTERVAL_REQ.INTREQ_DATE, SO_INTERVAL_REQ.INTREQ_TIME, SO_INTERVAL_REQ.INTREQ_TOTAL_REQ, SO_INTERVAL_REQ.INVTYP_ID, SO_INTERVAL_REQ.INTREQ_PEAK_TIME_INTERVAL, NVL(JOB.JOB_DESC, JOB.JOB_NAME) AS JOB_DESC FROM SO_INTERVAL_REQ, JOB, SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP WHERE SO_INTERVAL_REQ.JOB_ID = JOB.JOB_ID AND SO_INTERVAL_REQ.SKDGRP_ID = SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_ID

table.name: VIEW_SO_NET_STAFF
table.viewSql: SELECT VIEW_SO_NETSTFRAW.SKD_ID, VIEW_SO_NETSTFRAW.SKDGRP_ID, SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_NAME, VIEW_SO_NETSTFRAW.JOB_ID, NVL(JOB.JOB_DESC, JOB.JOB_NAME) AS JOB_DESC, VIEW_SO_NETSTFRAW.SKDSHFT_DATE, COUNT(*) AS NUM_ASSIGNED FROM VIEW_SO_NETSTFRAW, SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP, JOB WHERE VIEW_SO_NETSTFRAW.SKDGRP_ID = SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_ID AND VIEW_SO_NETSTFRAW.JOB_ID = JOB.JOB_ID GROUP BY VIEW_SO_NETSTFRAW.SKD_ID, VIEW_SO_NETSTFRAW.SKDGRP_ID, SKDGRP_NAME, VIEW_SO_NETSTFRAW.JOB_ID, JOB_DESC, JOB_NAME, SKDSHFT_DATE

table.name: VIEW_SO_NETSTF_REQ
table.viewSql: SELECT SO_SCHEDULED_SHIFT.SKD_ID, SO_SCHEDULED_SHIFT.SKDSHFT_DATE, SO_SHIFT_REQ.SKDGRP_ID, SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_NAME, SO_SHIFT_REQ.JOB_ID, NVL(JOB.JOB_DESC, JOB.JOB_NAME) AS JOB_DESC, SUM(SO_SHIFT_REQ.SHFTREQ_MIN_REQ) AS NUMBER_NEEDED FROM SO_SCHEDULED_SHIFT, SO_SHIFT_REQ, SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP, JOB WHERE SO_SCHEDULED_SHIFT.SKDSHFT_ID = SO_SHIFT_REQ.SKDSHFT_ID AND SO_SHIFT_REQ.JOB_ID = JOB.JOB_ID AND SO_SHIFT_REQ.SKDGRP_ID(+) = SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_ID GROUP BY SO_SCHEDULED_SHIFT.SKD_ID, SO_SHIFT_REQ.SKDGRP_ID, SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_NAME, SO_SHIFT_REQ.JOB_ID, JOB_DESC, JOB_NAME, SO_SCHEDULED_SHIFT.SKDSHFT_DATE

table.name: VIEW_SO_NETSTFRAW
table.viewSql: Select VIEW_SO_SCHED.SKD_ID, Case When VIEW_SO_SCHED.WRK_LOC is null Then VIEW_SO_SCHED.SKDGRP_ID else VIEW_SO_SCHED.WRK_LOC end as SKDGRP_ID, SO_EMPLOYEE.EMPGRP_ID, VIEW_SO_SCHED.EMP_ID, VIEW_SO_SCHED.JOB_ID, VIEW_SO_SCHED.SKDSHFT_DATE, 0 as NUM_NEEDED, 0 as STAFF_DIFF From VIEW_SO_SCHED, SO_EMPLOYEE Where VIEW_SO_SCHED.EMP_ID is not null AND VIEW_SO_SCHED.EMP_ID = SO_EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID (+)

table.name: VIEW_SO_POSPAY
table.viewSql: SELECT VIEW_SO_EMP_CSTDET.SKDGRP_ID, VIEW_SO_EMP_CSTDET.JOB_ID, NVL(JOB.JOB_DESC,JOB.JOB_NAME) AS JOB_DESC, WRKS_WORK_DATE, SUM(EMPLOYEE_PAY) AS EMPLOYEE_PAY, SUM(REG_HOURS) AS REG_HOURS, SUM(OT_HOURS) AS OT_HOURS FROM VIEW_SO_EMP_CSTDET, JOB WHERE VIEW_SO_EMP_CSTDET.JOB_ID(+) = JOB.JOB_ID GROUP BY VIEW_SO_EMP_CSTDET.SKDGRP_ID, VIEW_SO_EMP_CSTDET.JOB_ID, JOB_DESC, JOB_NAME, WRKS_WORK_DATE

table.name: VIEW_SO_PROD_RES
table.viewSql: SELECT SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_ID, SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_NAME, SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_PARENT_ID, SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.VOLTYP_ID, SO_VOLUME_TYPE.VOLTYP_DESC, CASE WHEN VIEW_SO_FCAST_DET.FCAST_ADJTYP = 2 THEN NVL(VIEW_SO_FCAST_DET.FCAST_CALLS,0) + NVL(VIEW_SO_FCAST_DET.FCAST_ADJVAL,0) ELSE NVL(VIEW_SO_FCAST_DET.FCAST_CALLS,0) + (NVL(VIEW_SO_FCAST_DET.FCAST_CALLS,0) * (NVL(VIEW_SO_FCAST_DET.FCAST_ADJVAL,0) / 100)) END AS FCAST_CALLS, SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_FCAST_MTD, NVL(VIEW_SO_DAY_RES.DAILY_VOLUME,0) AS DAILY_VOLUME, VIEW_SO_DAY_RES.RESDET_DATE, VIEW_SO_FCAST_DET.FCAST_DATE, NVL(REG_HOURS,0) AS REG_HOURS, NVL(OT_HOURS,0) AS OT_HOURS, NVL(REG_HOURS,0) + NVL(OT_HOURS,0) AS TOTAL_HOURS, NVL(EMPLOYEE_PAY,0) AS EMPLOYEE_PAY, 0 AS HOURLY_WAGE FROM SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP, SO_VOLUME_TYPE, VIEW_SO_DAY_RES, VIEW_SO_FCAST_DET, VIEW_SO_SKDGRP_PAY WHERE VIEW_SO_DAY_RES.SKDGRP_ID = SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_ID AND VIEW_SO_FCAST_DET.SKDGRP_ID = SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_ID AND VIEW_SO_DAY_RES.RESDET_DATE = VIEW_SO_FCAST_DET.FCAST_DATE AND VIEW_SO_SKDGRP_PAY.SKDGRP_ID = SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_ID AND VIEW_SO_DAY_RES.RESDET_DATE = VIEW_SO_SKDGRP_PAY.WRKS_WORK_DATE AND SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.VOLTYP_ID(+) = SO_VOLUME_TYPE.VOLTYP_ID

table.name: VIEW_SO_PROD_RESPS
table.viewSql: SELECT SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_ID, SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_NAME, JOB.JOB_ID, NVL(JOB.JOB_DESC, JOB.JOB_NAME) AS JOB_DESC, SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_PARENT_ID, SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.VOLTYP_ID, SO_VOLUME_TYPE.VOLTYP_DESC, CASE WHEN VIEW_SO_FCAST_DET.FCAST_ADJTYP = 2 THEN NVL(VIEW_SO_FCAST_DET.FCAST_CALLS,0) + NVL(VIEW_SO_FCAST_DET.FCAST_ADJVAL,0) ELSE NVL(VIEW_SO_FCAST_DET.FCAST_CALLS,0) + (NVL(VIEW_SO_FCAST_DET.FCAST_CALLS,0) * (NVL(VIEW_SO_FCAST_DET.FCAST_ADJVAL,0) / 100)) END AS FCAST_CALLS, SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_FCAST_MTD, NVL(VIEW_SO_DAY_RES.DAILY_VOLUME,0) AS DAILY_VOLUME, VIEW_SO_DAY_RES.RESDET_DATE, VIEW_SO_FCAST_DET.FCAST_DATE, NVL(REG_HOURS,0) AS REG_HOURS, NVL(OT_HOURS,0) AS OT_HOURS, NVL(REG_HOURS,0) + NVL(OT_HOURS,0) AS TOTAL_HOURS, NVL(EMPLOYEE_PAY,0) AS EMPLOYEE_PAY, NVL(JOB_TEAM.JOBTEAM_AV_HR_RATE,0) AS HOURLY_WAGE FROM JOB, VIEW_SO_POSPAY, JOB_TEAM, SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP, SO_VOLUME_TYPE, VIEW_SO_FCAST_DET, VIEW_SO_DAY_RES, WORKBRAIN_TEAM WHERE WORKBRAIN_TEAM.WBT_ID = SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.WBT_ID AND JOB_TEAM.WBT_ID = WORKBRAIN_TEAM.WBT_ID AND JOB.JOB_ID = JOB_TEAM.JOB_ID AND SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_ID = VIEW_SO_DAY_RES.SKDGRP_ID AND VIEW_SO_POSPAY.JOB_ID = JOB_TEAM.JOB_ID AND VIEW_SO_DAY_RES.RESDET_DATE = VIEW_SO_POSPAY.WRKS_WORK_DATE AND VIEW_SO_DAY_RES.RESDET_DATE = VIEW_SO_FCAST_DET.FCAST_DATE AND VIEW_SO_FCAST_DET.SKDGRP_ID = SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.SKDGRP_ID AND VIEW_SO_POSPAY.JOB_ID(+) = JOB.JOB_ID AND SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP.VOLTYP_ID(+) = SO_VOLUME_TYPE.VOLTYP_ID

table.name: VIEW_SO_SCHED
table.viewSql: SELECT SO_SCHEDULE.SKD_PUBLISHED, EMPLOYEE.EMP_FULLNAME AS EMP_NAME, EMPLOYEE.EMP_FIRSTNAME, EMPLOYEE.EMP_LASTNAME, EMPLOYEE.EMP_SENIORITY_DATE, SO_SCHEDULED_SHIFT.SKDSHFT_NAME, NVL(SO_EMPLOYEE_GROUP.EMPGRP_DESC, SO_EMPLOYEE_GROUP.EMPGRP_NAME) AS EMPGRP_DESC, SO_EMPLOYEE_GROUP.EMPGRP_ID, SO_SCHEDULED_SHIFT.SKDSHFT_DATE, SO_SCHEDULED_SHIFT.SKDSHFT_START_TIME, SO_SCHEDULED_SHIFT.SKDSHFT_END_TIME, SO_SCHEDULED_SHIFT.SKDSHFT_FIXED, SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SHFTDET_EDITED, SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SHFTDET_START_TIME, SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SHFTDET_END_TIME, SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SHFTDET_USE_TIME, CASE WHEN SHFTDET_USE_TIME = 1 THEN SHFTDET_START_TIME ELSE SKDSHFT_START_TIME END AS STF_START_TIME, CASE WHEN SHFTDET_USE_TIME = 1 THEN SHFTDET_END_TIME ELSE SKDSHFT_END_TIME END AS STF_END_TIME, CASE WHEN SHFTDET_END_TIME <= SHFTDET_START_TIME THEN TO_NUMBER(TO_CHAR((SHFTDET_END_TIME - SHFTDET_START_TIME + 1) * 24, '99999.99')) ELSE TO_NUMBER(TO_CHAR((SHFTDET_END_TIME - SHFTDET_START_TIME) * 24, '99999.99')) END AS EGSR_SHIFT_LEN, CASE WHEN (SHFTDET_END_TIME <= SHFTDET_START_TIME AND TO_CHAR(SHFTDET_END_TIME,'HH24:MI:SS') <> '00:00:00' AND TO_CHAR(SHFTDET_START_TIME,'HH24:MI:SS') <> '00:00:00' AND SHFTDET_USE_TIME = 1) OR (SKDSHFT_END_TIME <= SKDSHFT_START_TIME AND TO_CHAR(SKDSHFT_END_TIME,'HH24:MI:SS') <> '00:00:00' AND TO_CHAR(SKDSHFT_START_TIME,'HH24:MI:SS') <> '00:00:00' AND SHFTDET_USE_TIME <> 1) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS MIDNIGHT_ROLLOVER, SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SHFTDET_RATE, SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SKD_ID, SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.EMP_ID, SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.JOB_ID AS JOB_ID, SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SHFTDET_ID, SO_SCHEDULED_SHIFT.SKDSHFT_ID, SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SHFTDET_WRK_LOC AS WRK_LOC, SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SHFTDET_WRK_LOC AS SKDGRP_ID FROM SO_SHIFT_DETAIL, EMPLOYEE, SO_SCHEDULED_SHIFT, SO_EMPLOYEE, SO_EMPLOYEE_GROUP, SO_SCHEDULE WHERE SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SKDSHFT_ID = SO_SCHEDULED_SHIFT.SKDSHFT_ID AND SO_SCHEDULE.SKD_ID = SO_SCHEDULED_SHIFT.SKD_ID AND SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SKD_ID = SO_SCHEDULED_SHIFT.SKD_ID AND SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SKD_ID = SO_SCHEDULE.SKD_ID AND SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.EMP_ID = EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID (+) AND EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID = SO_EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID (+) AND SO_EMPLOYEE.EMPGRP_ID = SO_EMPLOYEE_GROUP.EMPGRP_ID (+)

table.name: VIEW_SO_SCHED_GRP

table.name: VIEW_SO_SKDEMP_POS
table.viewSql: SELECT NVL(SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SHFTDET_WRK_LOC, SO_SCHEDULE.SKDGRP_ID) AS SKDGRP_ID, SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SKD_ID, SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SHFTDET_ID, SO_SCHEDULED_SHIFT.SKDSHFT_DATE , SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SHFTDET_START_TIME, SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SHFTDET_END_TIME, SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.EMP_ID, CASE WHEN SO_EMPLOYEE.SEMP_ONFIXED_SKD = 1 AND SO_EMPLOYEE.SEMP_IS_SALARY = 1 THEN 24 ELSE TO_NUMBER(TO_CHAR(NVL(JOB_TEAM.JOBTEAM_DOT_THRESH,0), '999999.99')) END AS JOBTEAM_DOT_THRESH FROM SO_SHIFT_DETAIL, SO_EMPLOYEE, EMPLOYEE_JOB, JOB_TEAM, SO_SCHEDULED_SHIFT, SO_SCHEDULE WHERE SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SKDSHFT_ID = SO_SCHEDULED_SHIFT.SKDSHFT_ID AND SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SKD_ID = SO_SCHEDULE.SKD_ID AND EMPLOYEE_JOB.JOB_ID = JOB_TEAM.JOB_ID AND SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.EMP_ID = SO_EMPLOYEE.EMP_ID (+) AND SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.EMP_ID = EMPLOYEE_JOB.EMP_ID (+)

table.name: VIEW_SO_SKDEMPACT
table.viewSql: SELECT NVL(SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SKDGRP_ID, SO_SCHEDULE.SKDGRP_ID) AS SKDGRP_ID, SO_SCHEDULE.SKD_PUBLISHED, SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SKD_ID, SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.EMP_ID, SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.JOB_ID, SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SHFTDET_ID, SO_SCHEDULED_SHIFT.SKDSHFT_DATE AS SKDSHFT_DATE, SO_SHIFT_ACTIVITY.SHFTACT_DATE, SO_SHIFT_ACTIVITY.SHFTACT_START_TIME, SO_SHIFT_ACTIVITY.SHFTACT_END_TIME, SO_SHIFT_ACTIVITY.SHFTACT_ID, SO_ACTIVITY.ACT_PAID, SO_ACTIVITY.ACT_WORKING, SO_ACTIVITY.ACT_CONT_TO_COST, CASE WHEN SHFTACT_END_TIME - SHFTACT_START_TIME <= 0 THEN TO_NUMBER(TO_CHAR((SHFTACT_END_TIME - SHFTACT_START_TIME + 1) * 24, '99999.99'), '99999.99') ELSE TO_NUMBER(TO_CHAR((SHFTACT_END_TIME - SHFTACT_START_TIME) * 24, '99999.99'), '99999.99') END AS SHFTACT_LEN FROM SO_SHIFT_DETAIL, SO_SCHEDULED_SHIFT, SO_SCHEDULE, SO_SHIFT_ACTIVITY, SO_ACTIVITY WHERE SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SKDSHFT_ID = SO_SCHEDULED_SHIFT.SKDSHFT_ID AND SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SKD_ID = SO_SCHEDULE.SKD_ID AND SO_SHIFT_DETAIL.SHFTDET_ID = SO_SHIFT_ACTIVITY.SHFTDET_ID AND SO_SHIFT_ACTIVITY.ACT_ID = SO_ACTIVITY.ACT_ID

table.name: VIEW_SO_SKDGRP_PAY
table.viewSql: SELECT SKDGRP_ID, WRKS_WORK_DATE, SUM(EMPLOYEE_PAY) AS EMPLOYEE_PAY, SUM(REG_HOURS) AS REG_HOURS, SUM(OT_HOURS) AS OT_HOURS FROM VIEW_SO_EMP_CSTDET GROUP BY SKDGRP_ID, WRKS_WORK_DATE

table.viewSql:
SELECT ROOT.WBT_ID IN_WBT_ID, 'Y' AS IN_INCL_SUBTEAM, SUB.WBT_ID OUT_WBT_ID, SUB.WBT_LFT OUT_WBT_LFT, SUB.WBT_RGT OUT_WBT_RGT FROM WORKBRAIN_TEAM ROOT INNER JOIN WORKBRAIN_TEAM SUB ON ROOT.WBT_LFT <= SUB.WBT_LFT AND SUB.WBT_RGT <= ROOT.WBT_RGT
UNION ALL

table.name: VIEW_WBI_LOCATION_DIMENSION
table.viewSql: SELECT SKDGRP_CHILD.SKDGRP_ID SKDGRP_ID, SKDGRP_CHILD.WBT_ID WBT_ID, SKDGRP_PARENT.SKDGRP_ID STORE_SKDGRP_ID, WBT_PARENT.WBT_ID STORE_WBT_ID, SKDGRP_PARENT.SKDGRP_NAME STORE_NAME, CASE WHEN SKDGRP_CHILD.SKDGRP_INTRNL_TYPE = 11 THEN SKDGRP_CHILD.SKDGRP_NAME ELSE 'N/A' END DEPARTMENT_NAME, CASE WHEN SKDGRP_CHILD.SKDGRP_INTRNL_TYPE = 12 THEN SKDGRP_CHILD.SKDGRP_NAME ELSE 'N/A' END DRIVER_NAME FROM SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP SKDGRP_CHILD, WORKBRAIN_TEAM WBT_PARENT, WORKBRAIN_TEAM WBT_CHILD, SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP SKDGRP_PARENT WHERE SKDGRP_CHILD.WBT_ID = WBT_CHILD.WBT_ID AND SKDGRP_PARENT.WBT_ID = WBT_PARENT.WBT_ID AND WBT_CHILD.WBT_LFT BETWEEN WBT_PARENT.WBT_LFT AND WBT_PARENT.WBT_RGT AND WBT_CHILD.WBT_RGT BETWEEN WBT_PARENT.WBT_LFT AND WBT_PARENT.WBT_RGT AND SKDGRP_PARENT.SKDGRP_INTRNL_TYPE = 10 AND SKDGRP_CHILD.SKDGRP_PARENT_ID = SKDGRP_PARENT.SKDGRP_ID AND SKDGRP_CHILD.SKDGRP_INTRNL_TYPE IN (11, 12) UNION ALL SELECT SKDGRP_PARENT.SKDGRP_ID SKDGRP_ID, WBT_PARENT.WBT_ID WBT_ID, SKDGRP_PARENT.SKDGRP_ID STORE_SKDGRP_ID, WBT_PARENT.WBT_ID STORE_WBT_ID, SKDGRP_PARENT.SKDGRP_NAME STORE_NAME, 'N/A' DEPARTMENT_NAME, 'N/A' DRIVER_NAME FROM WORKBRAIN_TEAM WBT_PARENT, SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP SKDGRP_PARENT WHERE SKDGRP_PARENT.WBT_ID = WBT_PARENT.WBT_ID AND SKDGRP_PARENT.SKDGRP_INTRNL_TYPE = 10 AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM SO_SCHEDULE_GROUP SKDGRP, WORKBRAIN_TEAM WBT WHERE SKDGRP.WBT_ID = WBT.WBT_ID AND WBT.WBT_LFT BETWEEN WBT_PARENT.WBT_LFT AND WBT_PARENT.WBT_RGT AND WBT.WBT_RGT BETWEEN WBT_PARENT.WBT_LFT AND WBT_PARENT.WBT_RGT AND SKDGRP_PARENT.SKDGRP_ID = SKDGRP.SKDGRP_PARENT_ID AND SKDGRP.SKDGRP_INTRNL_TYPE IN (11, 12) )

table.name: WBI_SEC_EMP_BY_TEAM
table.viewSql:
SELECT VIEWABLE_SUBTEAMS.IN_WBU_ID, VIEWABLE_SUBTEAMS.IN_WBT_ID, VIEWABLE_SUBTEAMS.IN_INCL_SUBTEAMS,
ET.EMP_ID, GREATEST (ET.EMPT_START_DATE, VIEWABLE_SUBTEAMS.WFUT_START_DATE), LEAST (ET.EMPT_END_DATE, VIEWABLE_SUBTEAMS.WFUT_END_DATE), VIEWABLE_SUBTEAMS.OUT_WBT_ID, ET.EMPT_HOME_TEAM
FROM EMPLOYEE_TEAM ET INNER JOIN (SELECT VIEW_SUBTEAMS.OUT_WBT_ID, VIEW_SUBTEAMS.IN_WBT_ID, VIEW_SUBTEAMS.IN_INCL_SUBTEAMS, USER_PERM.WFUT_START_DATE, USER_PERM.WFUT_END_DATE, USER_PERM.EMP_ID USER_EMP_ID, USER_PERM.IN_WBU_ID FROM
VIEW_SUBTEAMS
INNER JOIN
-- user team record with extra user and team data. (SELECT WT.WBT_LFT, WT.WBT_RGT, UUT.IN_WBU_ID, UUT.EMP_ID, UUT.WFUT_START_DATE, UUT.WFUT_END_DATE FROM WORKBRAIN_TEAM WT INNER JOIN -- Tie users to user team records (SELECT U.WBU_ID IN_WBU_ID, U.EMP_ID, UT.WBT_ID, UT.WFUT_START_DATE, UT.WFUT_END_DATE FROM WORKBRAIN_USER U INNER JOIN WBI_FLAT_USER_TEAM UT ON U.WBU_ID = UT.WBU_ID ) UUT ON UUT.WBT_ID = WT.WBT_ID ) USER_PERM
-- Choose from the selected teams only those that are subteams of the root viewable teams. ON USER_PERM.WBT_LFT <= VIEW_SUBTEAMS.OUT_WBT_LFT AND VIEW_SUBTEAMS.OUT_WBT_RGT <= USER_PERM.WBT_RGT ) VIEWABLE_SUBTEAMS
ON ET.WBT_ID = VIEWABLE_SUBTEAMS.OUT_WBT_ID AND ET.EMPT_START_DATE <= VIEWABLE_SUBTEAMS.WFUT_END_DATE AND ET.EMPT_END_DATE >= VIEWABLE_SUBTEAMS.WFUT_START_DATE AND ET.EMP_ID <> VIEWABLE_SUBTEAMS.USER_EMP_ID UNION ALL
-- If the user can see themselves, then load the employee team records of that employee for -- the team (or subteams) specified in the input.
SELECT WORKBRAIN_USER.WBU_ID, VIEW_SUBTEAMS.IN_WBT_ID, VIEW_SUBTEAMS.IN_INCL_SUBTEAMS,
EMPLOYEE_TEAM.EMP_ID, EMPLOYEE_TEAM.EMPT_START_DATE, EMPLOYEE_TEAM.EMPT_END_DATE, EMPLOYEE_TEAM.WBT_ID, EMPLOYEE_TEAM.EMPT_HOME_TEAM
FROM WORKBRAIN_USER, EMPLOYEE_TEAM, VIEW_SUBTEAMS
WHERE WORKBRAIN_USER.EMP_ID = EMPLOYEE_TEAM.EMP_ID AND WORKBRAIN_USER.WBU_CANSEE_SELF = 'Y' AND EMPLOYEE_TEAM.WBT_ID = VIEW_SUBTEAMS.OUT_WBT_ID
